{"title":"“落日梅”（诗四首）","authors":["晓报"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":1,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“落日梅”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（诗四首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云南省铁路工人　晓报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军磨刀石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯弯的南盘江的桥头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块磨刀石青幽幽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十几年前红军在上面磨过战刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“红军磨刀石”五个大字永不生锈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯弯的南盘江桥头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日铁道兵歌声吼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蘸干盘江水磨利钢钎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁路顺着红军的脚印修。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“落日梅”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红似火把的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是山顶的茶花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香味扑鼻的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是山脚下的缅桂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但这些都比不上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半山腰的“落日梅”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳刚刚落下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁道兵从工地返回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰隆隆的连珠炮响了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火花映照着落日的余辉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半个山让开路了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“落日梅”和晚霞比美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么好的夜呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在云贵高原上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我们点起了篝火；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愉快的劳动过后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躺在帐棚里歇脚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星星守望着我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮和我们谈说；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子拉着二胡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘唱起家乡的情歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯光和星星相连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像落下了天上的银河；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么美丽的夜呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么好的生活！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱民站"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热闹的工地旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士搭起棚帐："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“阿妈走路累了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝杯香茶心舒畅！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“阿爹请吸一锅旱烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表一表儿子的心肠！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿妈咻动着嘴后不说话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地摸着战士的领章。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}